{"tid":1026903,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 全軍破敵:戰鎚2","createTime":"2019-02-18T12:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T15:23:31.000Z","uid":53515,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f271427886d308337af886fcf1c2840eaee19d9d","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"對厭了中世紀，殺悶了德軍？<br />\n也許　<span style=\"color: orange;\">《全軍破敵:戰鎚2》</span>係你另一個選擇<br />\n<br />\n希望係戰埸可以見到巴打一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ST9D3C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FST9D3C2.jpg&h=8bc53378&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全軍破敵:戰鎚2　<br />\n再沒有冷兵器嘅限制，帶入魔法及飛龍等魔幻生物，令戰埸不再單調<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rUB7cyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrUB7cyb.png&h=1e905587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\nＰＶＰ視頻介紹<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a0d-C99veys&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da0d-C99veys%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=87f9cba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a0d-C99veys&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今集種族有&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n人類<br />\n吸血鬼<br />\n木精靈<br />\n布塔妮亞<br />\n矮人<br />\n混沌武士<br />\n野獸人<br />\n高精靈<br />\n暗精靈<br />\n蜥蝪人<br />\n古墓王<br />\n喪屍海盜<br />\n<br />\n地圖如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1sBQiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1sBQiK.jpg&h=0fe26eef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n接下來我會逐一介紹唔同種族　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce80e2d4e109b25813ae8f24bb8b30710edc2dd","tid":1026903,"uid":7292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"出文好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1d528d5cab24e61b894c1babf90b94fb483dfa","tid":1026903,"uid":3039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"邊個比你打機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c068313c98067188f9c0a090b5e6a733b78d36","tid":1026903,"uid":108606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:22:15.000Z","msg":"出文啦屌你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無文無人權唔准打機呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b217e77bcf83a5d4b86e026ce9dc883e8defb1","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解你哋會知　今日咪出咗囉　比我打機啦　好耐冇人陪我玩"},{"pid":"f1015a50bf761d15ae2170f115eb92320d13348f","tid":1026903,"uid":93062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚鍾意玩高精avalon魔法箭屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93c49c06ac97491abde4e910bfc1aa32b95b4df","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">帝國　Empire</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7UCqJLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7UCqJLJ.jpg&h=fe328fa2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\nPVP出現率    :☆☆★★★<br />\n軍隊完整度    :★★★★★<br />\n地形依賴        :☆☆☆★★<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">優點</span>&mdash;<br />\n兵種完善　可以認付不同對手<br />\n大炮匹敵矮人，騎兵不輸布塔妮亞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">缺點</span>&mdash;<br />\n步兵士氣低，容易被擊潰<br />\n遠程步兵弱<br />\n空軍弱<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n小結&mdash;<br />\n新手種族，因為單位便宜，能以量取勝，容錯率高<br />\n但打ranking1300以上時缺乏精英單位，難以出奇制勝"},{"pid":"362bfd571b37b12ba507bf0afd51aa3744475bd6","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1015a50bf761d15ae2170f115eb92320d13348f","tid":1026903,"uid":93062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚鍾意玩高精avalon魔法箭屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fOcPIEyW2g&amp;t=359s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6fOcPIEyW2g%26t%3D359s&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=c74eeaba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fOcPIEyW2g&amp;t=359s</a>"},{"pid":"4d76105df373e46c2314911f2dd9f39c67ae9975","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">布塔妮亞　Bretonnia</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xtkf521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtkf521.jpg&h=1d7a11d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nPVP出現率 :☆☆☆★★<br />\n軍隊完整度 :☆☆☆★★<br />\n地形依賴 　:☆☆☆☆★<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n優點&mdash;<br />\n強大騎兵單位<br />\n絕對制空權<br />\n軍隊主動性強<br />\n<br />\n缺點&mdash;<br />\n步兵出奇地差<br />\n騎兵續戰力弱<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n小結&mdash;<br />\n高手種族　ｒａｎｋｉｎｇ比較少見<br />\nBretonnia　需求玩家有良好嘅攻擊意識（利用樹林／高低坡隱藏騎兵，對敵人發動攻擊）<br />\n中價騎兵（＄７００）弱，連重甲步兵都打唔過，只有重甲騎兵（＄１６００）值得投資<br />\n兵步線如同虛設，好考你主唔主導到戰埸，各方配合攻擊"},{"pid":"b15686fa6a0ab3402c0881148f689fcb58d022e9","tid":1026903,"uid":198245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"視頻？"},{"pid":"32da314fae5086b988c84dbb5571d41d350943a6","tid":1026903,"uid":118781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"用唔用SFO 玩?"},{"pid":"02382daf8eb9d8f976948d3472f265b88ac8d407","tid":1026903,"uid":3039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"視你老母頻 影片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9352c2fc143762882b810a9aebecc497d12a1d35","tid":1026903,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"玩緊第一代，但唔識將2個領主合歸一隊，只可合士兵"},{"pid":"d57d02ef43cf4b5037d85602dda7c80e79e72b70","tid":1026903,"uid":118781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9352c2fc143762882b810a9aebecc497d12a1d35","tid":1026903,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"玩緊第一代，但唔識將2個領主合歸一隊，只可合士兵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"warhammer 系列一group 只可以有1個lord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65d40d20a986c71c0b7451dbd0fb14c62f023c3","tid":1026903,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57d02ef43cf4b5037d85602dda7c80e79e72b70","tid":1026903,"uid":118781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9352c2fc143762882b810a9aebecc497d12a1d35","tid":1026903,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"玩緊第一代，但唔識將2個領主合歸一隊，只可合士兵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"warhammer 系列一group 只可以有1個lord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"電腦可以控2個咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d787338249714f4c8a8449716b3cdf66b547fd","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">高精靈 High Elf</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xTpZqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xTpZqk.jpg&h=7e62bb3f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nPVP出現率 :☆★★★★<br />\n軍隊完整度 :★★★★★<br />\n地形依賴 　:☆☆★★★<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n優點&mdash;<br />\n兵種完善　可以應對唔同對手<br />\n空中單位次於Bretonnia，有龍，鳳凰等特殊單位<br />\n步兵質素高，（鳳凰守衛／荷斯劍聖）<br />\n弓兵質素最高&mdash;<br />\n自帶矛盾，可作近戰兵使用，自保力極強<br />\n阿瓦隆姊妹，全遊戲弓兵輸出最高單位<br />\n<br />\n不依賴地形，可主打騎兵搶弓，可買弩炮打陣地戰<br />\n<br />\n缺點&mdash;<br />\n好撚貴！<br />\n最平嘅矛兵都要５００，重裝步兵如鳳凰守衛要１４００<br />\n龍要２４００<br />\n重騎兵又要１６００<br />\n弓兵又要１３００<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n小結&mdash;<br />\n高精靈適合新／中手玩　建設新玩家用佢打單人戰役<br />\nｐｖｐ時小心評估對手，如地圖山多，你就唔好買騎兵，轉買飛龍<br />\n對手係矮人就買多啲破甲單位，如劍聖<br />\n<br />\n因為兵種太貴，你買錯兵的話未打已經輸咗"},{"pid":"37315efad001996a2aa7360a42d4d2177a860fee","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02382daf8eb9d8f976948d3472f265b88ac8d407","tid":1026903,"uid":3039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"視你老母頻 影片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2d42f9f7f62bd2550c0398b09f660615a9d51a","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65d40d20a986c71c0b7451dbd0fb14c62f023c3","tid":1026903,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu