:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57d02ef43cf4b5037d85602dda7c80e79e72b70","tid":1026903,"uid":118781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"warhammer 系列一group 只可以有1個lord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"電腦可以控2個咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"AI分開2個group用reinforcement入,  你都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"btw隻game平衡咁撚柒差都好去玩pvp?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔用overhaul mod大改就算送隻game俾我狗都唔撚會去屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dc78bae0ab9bed9e4eaaecd0ca970638737d18","tid":1026903,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">吸血鬼海岸　Vampire coast</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfmSoXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfmSoXq.jpg&h=3738b2f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nPVP出現率 :☆☆☆★★<br />\n軍隊完整度 :☆☆☆☆★<br />\n地形依賴 　:★★★★★<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">優點&mdash;</span><br />\n大炮<br />\n大炮<br />\n大炮<br />\n步槍<br />\n步槍<br />\n步槍<br />\n壓倒性遠程火力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">缺點&mdash;</span><br />\n近戰步兵質素低<br />\n缺乏騎兵　戰局被動<br />\n極度依賴地形，因為海盜只有槍械兵，<span style=\"color: red;\">必須要由高位攻擊，否則企係自己步兵後面係唔會開火</span><br />\n所以吸血鬼海岸一定要係山上佈陣<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n小結&mdash;<br />\n吸血鬼海岸適合高手玩　建設新玩家用佢打單人戰役<br />\n<br />\n因為佢太食地形，你一定要對敵人及自己軍隊能力有好好理解先可以贏<br />\n只要你佈好個陣已經贏一半<br />\n但你唔識利用地形／評估錯敵手　你未打已經輸<br />\n<br />\n例子：敵手&mdash;　Bretonnia　地形&mdash;山谷<br />\n你買好多大炮，打算射撚死佢啲騎兵海，但係你發現佢玩空軍，你未開炮已經比佢啲空降騎兵殺哂你嘅大炮，你就ＧＧ了"},{"pid":"059a4040ed6b031322db75dbc0274165f1ef